ygData.messageBody:
I believe you may be thinking of Paineel, and The Hole. Those are
near Tox forrest. Of which I believe they will be adding soon. I
have no idea where Temple of Solusek Ro is, although I am patching
them even as I type this and I just got a file called lavastorm, so
the previous post about it being in that zone seems to make sense.
